### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:6002/health


###


### 1. 文件上传接口 - 上传音频文件
POST http://localhost:6002/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./uploads/2026-03-17/test01_audio_1773756575209.webm
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--


###


### 2. 文件上传并语音识别 - 一站式接口
POST http://localhost:6002/asr/filetotext
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.webm"
Content-Type: audio/webm

< ./uploads/2026-03-17/test01_audio_1773756575209.webm
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="model"

qwen3-asr-flash-filetrans
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="diarization_enabled"

true
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="speaker_count"

2
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--


###


### 3. 通过URL进行语音识别
POST http://localhost:6002/asr/url
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url": "https://dashscope.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/samples/audio/sensevoice/rich_text_example_1.wav",
    "model": "qwen3-asr-flash-filetrans",
    "diarization_enabled": false,
    "speaker_count": 1
}


###


### 4. 查询任务状态
# 请将 your-task-id 替换为实际的 task id
GET http://localhost:6002/asr/task/your-task-id


###


### 5. 获取上传的文件（文件访问服务）
GET http://localhost:6002/uploads/2026-03-17/test01_audio_1773756575209.webm
